description:
This classic Christmas centrepiece won the Silver medal in the 2022 Royal Tasmanian Fine Food Awards. A symphony of flavours come together in this Christmas centrepiece with hints of smokiness, sweet honey and fig. We've smoked this tender juicy ham with mountain ash wood and sourced the honey in our sticky glaze from the Northern Rivers region of NSW to create a sensational, easy-to-carve main that stands out on the table.
 Made in Australia by SunPork Fresh Foods who are owned and operated by three Australian families. The SunPork Fresh Foods team have a farming history which dates back over three generations and combines more than 100 years of experience in pig farming. They produce exceptional pork products by controlling the entire supply chain from farm to plate to protect the quality of their pork.
Click here to discover more products in our Gold range, exclusively for Woolworths.
Oven Baking Instructions 

1) Preheat oven to 220 째C (Fan Forced 200 째C).  Remove all the contents from the box. 
2. Remove boneless ham from plastic bag and discard. 
3) Diagonally score the surface of the boneless ham. Place on the foil tray, cover with aluminum foil, and place in the oven. 
4) Oven bake for 30 minutes at 220 째C (Fan Forced 200 째C). 
5) Remove from the oven and apply half of the ham glaze evenly over the yop of the ham joint. Place back in the oven uncovered for 15 minutes. 
6) Remove from the oven and apply the remainder of the ham glaze evenly over the top of the ham joint. Return to oven again uncovered for 15 minutes. 
7) Slice and serve.
name: Woolworths Gold Honey Fig & Rosemary Glaze & Bake Leg Ham 840g
